# AIBI Computer Vision for Manufacturing

A computer vision project for manufacturing applications using **uv** for dependency management.

## Project Structure

```
├── src/aibi_cv/          # Main package
├── tests/                # Test files
├── tools/                # Helper scripts
├── docs/                 # Documentation
│   ├── meetings/         # Meeting notes
│   ├── requirements/     # Requirements docs
│   └── questions/        # Project questions
├── examples/             # Runnable examples
│   ├── face_recognition/ # Face recognition demo
│   └── qr/              # QR code processing
├── data/                 # Local dev data (git ignored)
└── outputs/              # Generated outputs (git ignored)
```

## Getting Started

### 1. Install uv
https://docs.astral.sh/uv/getting-started/installation/

```bash
# Linux/macOS
curl -LsSf https://astral.sh/uv/install.sh | sh

# Windows
powershell -ExecutionPolicy ByPass -c "irm https://astral.sh/uv/install.ps1 | iex"
```

### 2. Install dependencies
```bash
uv sync
```

### 3. Run examples
```bash

# QR code example
uv run python examples/qr/simple_qr_scanner.py
```
